Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  看到了吗  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再做一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是冬天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全进入冬天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  热乎点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
